e 6--Projections of Inflation. Note: Blue Chip CPI projection adjusted to PCE basis. Source: U.S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Economic Analysis; Blue Chip survey; Federal Open Market Committee (FOMC) projections. Blue Chip survey projections are taken from Blue Chip Economic Indicators, a publication owned by Aspen Publishers. ### Unemployment Rate. ## Figure 8--Simple Policy Rules. ### Unemployment Rate. ## Figure 9--Uncertainty and Policy Conditionality. ### Unemployment Rate.",
